🚨 FIGHTER PROFILE 🚨 

This one is all about Melissa Gatto. @melissagattomma

Melissa Gatto Regonha, born in1996 is a Brazilian professional mixed martial artist who currently fights in the women's flyweight division of the UFC. 

In the early parts of her professional career, Mellisa fought in numerous organisations in the regional circuit. 

Making her professional debut in December of 2016, Mellisa took on Alexandra Alves which she won via UD. This win set Mellisa up perfectly going into her next bout. 

Melissa racked up 5 wins and 1 draw without any losses before taking on Sidy Rocha for the PFC Flyweiht Championship. The bout ended in a draw which was the 2nd draw of Gatto's pro career. Just 2 months later Mellisa got back to winning ways defeating Karol Rosa via Submission [Kimura]. 

The impressive undefeated streak with a record of 6-0-2, Mellisa caught the eye of Dana White and the UFC. In 2018, Gatto made her UFC debut against Victoria Leonardo, she won via TKO. 

Melissa then took on Sijara Eubanks, once again Mellisa won via KO [body kick & punches]. She also won the performance of the night bonus.

She was then lined up to take on Tracy Cortez at UFC 274 in May 2022. It was not to be for Melissa as she suffered her first defeat a pro, losing via UD. 

We eaglerly await who's next for Melissa after she has recovered from her recent surgery.

#MelissaGatto #Brazil #BrazilMMA #Bjj #UFC #Fight #Knockout
